metadata.name: SAW Games Prize - Hand #1
metadata.description:
SAW Games Prizes - Hand is an official Autograph NFT as part of the SAW Games Prizes Collection. This NFT grants the holder the opportunity to have their name appear in the next SAW film. To redeem, the holder must link the non-custodial wallet holding this NFT to an Autograph.io account and hold the NFT in the linked non-custodial wallet as of November 17, 2022 3:00pm ET. 

After the deadline of November 17, 2022 3:00pm ET passes, if the qualifying owner transfers this NFT to a new holder, the new holder is not granted any utility mentioned above.

By receiving this NFT, the holder agrees to Autographâ€™s Terms Of Service (https://go.autograph.io/tos) and the Terms & Conditions specific to this NFT (https://terms.Autograph.io/saw2022internetgame.pdf) and the Game Rules (https://terms.autograph.io/SAW2022GameRules.pdf).

nft_collection.name: SAW Games Prizes Collection
nft_collection.description: SAW Games Prizes Collection is a limited edition of commemorative and prize NFTs, distributed by Autograph, for players who participated in Internet Game's SAW-themed mini-game tournament.
